name: 拉塞尔·多纳休
name_full: 拉塞尔·多纳休 Russel Donahue
introduction: Russel Donahue has become recognized as an exceptionally versatile actor from his leading roles as Wesley in the award-winning film, Dustlicker, and as Ace O'Connor in the award-winning film Shadow Farm. His vulnerable dramatic roles and quirky comedic parts are portrayed with deep emotional commitment found only in a rare few. He just recently finished filming a new comedy starring veteran actor Sean O'Bryan where he played Stanley, an annoying assistant to O'Bryan's wife. Donahue just starred in a sci-fi film that will be released this year. He will also be appearing in the feature Dustslickers where he will be once again playing the lead role of Wesley with a star studded cast.
